  <h1>Université de Montréal Alumni Interview Series</h1>

  <p>
    As part of Québec Meets NYC, I collaborated with Université de Montréal to highlight the impact of its alumni living and working in New York City.
  </p>

  <p>
    The goal was to showcase Québec talent abroad through personal stories, career journeys, and the international reach of UdeM graduates.
  </p>

  <p>
    Through this series, I created bilingual content that connected education, professional growth, and Québec’s presence in New York.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h2>The Concept</h2>

  <p>
    I developed a video interview format featuring UdeM alumni based in NYC, focusing on their path from Québec to New York and the role their education played in their journey.
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>Bilingual alumni storytelling</li>
    <li>Short-form video content for social media</li>
    <li>Long-form interviews hosted on YouTube</li>
    <li>Content designed for LinkedIn, Instagram, Facebook, and YouTube</li>
  </ul>

